    Bootstrap Nav
----------------------
It provides an easy and quick way to create basic navigation.

use .nav class

By default navs are left-aligned.
we can align to center or right

use class "nav justify-content-center/right"



<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Nav demo</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<nav class="nav justify-content-center">
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Product</a>
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Customer</a>
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Orders</a>


</nav>
</div>
</body>
</html>

------------------
we can display nav vertically by using classes
use .flex-column class for vertical

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Nav demo</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<nav class="nav justify-content-center flex-column">
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Product</a>
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Customer</a>
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Orders</a>


</nav>
</div>
</body>
</html>
-----------------
basic tabs
-------------------
to display tabs use class .nav-tabs

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Nav demo</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<nav class="nav nav-tabs">
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Product</a>
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Customer</a>
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Orders</a>


</nav>
</div>
</body>
</html>

---------------
Pills nav
----------------
we can create pills based navigation by using the class .nav-pills.

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Nav demo</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<nav class="nav nav-pills">
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Product</a>
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Customer</a>
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Orders</a>


</nav>
</div>
</body>
</html>

--------------

Bootstrap nav with drop down menus
-------------------------------------------------------
we can add dropdown menus to a link .
use the classes .dropdown, .dropdown-toggle, .dropdown-menu and .dropdown-item are required along with .nav, .nav-tabs or nav-pills.


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Nav demo</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<nav class="nav nav-tabs">
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Product</a>
<div class="nav-item dropdown">
<a href="#" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">Dropdown</a>
<div class="dropdown-menu">
<ol>
<a href="#" class="dropdown-item">Product1</a>
<a href="#" class="dropdown-item">Product2</a>
<a href="#" class="dropdown-item">Product3</a>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Customer</a>
<a href="#" class="nav-item nav-link">Orders</a>

</nav>
</div>
</body>
</html>
-----------------------

